50|$|<b>Valaciclovir</b> was {{approved}} {{for medical use}} in 1995. It is marketed by GlaxoSmithKline under the trade names Valtrex and Zelitrex. <b>Valaciclovir</b> has been available as a generic drug in the U.S. since November 25, 2009.|$|E
