40|$|<b>Valaciclovir</b> {{is rapidly}} and {{extensively}} converted to acyclovir. In {{this study we}} investigated the potential interaction between oral <b>valaciclovir</b> and Maalox. On each of three occasions 18 healthy volunteers received a single oral dose of 1000 mg <b>valaciclovir,</b> or 30 mL Maalox 65 min after <b>valaciclovir</b> administration, or 30 mL Maalox 30 min before <b>valaciclovir.</b> Acyclovir plasma concentrations and pharmacokinetic parameters were not significantly affected by administration of Maalox before or after <b>valaciclovir.</b> Therefore, {{there is no need}} for restriction of <b>valaciclovir</b> dosing in patients receiving antacid medication...|$|E
